name: Comic Page Print
description: Love a page so much you need to have it on your wall? Now you can! Simply leave the name, date, or description of the page you'd like during the checkout process. Or we can figure it out in emails. Whatever works for ya'! Double-Page Prints In some cases, two stacked pages look even better than one (like Lofty Ambitions or Traveler's Lullaby). You're getting a nearly poster-sized print for just $15 more (balance invoiced separately)... without any additional costs in shipping! PRODUCT INFO 8-color print on 100% cotton rag matte paper. An upgrade to a heavier fine art quality paper is available for $10 more ($25 for tall prints). Single Page Prints are 8.5x11 in. Two-Page Stack are approx 11x17 in. Image sizes are approx 10 inches wide. Shipped safely and handsomely in a crystal clear sleeve against heavy black mountboard in a bend-proof mailer. Signed, sealed, delivered!

name: Original Custom Art
description: How about an original one of a kind drawing for you savvy collector types? You can request any of your favorite characters or duos from One Swoop Fell, and I'll come up with some sort of scene to put them in. Or, if you have an idea of your own, feel free to shoot it by me. Simply make your request in the "Instructions to Seller" box during Checkout. Or email me if you miss that step. The drawings are penciled and inked on roughly postcard-sized watercolor paper. Then it's stamped with a handmade seal so you'll know it's original and by me! Watercolor Art (and other options): For an extra $20 you can have your art in color! Contact me and I'll invoice you the balance. Please allow up to two weeks for delivery since the art and seal needs time to completely dry! NOTE: The image above is an example, and not for sale!

name: Happy BIRDthay Greeting Card
description:
Put your party hats on, there's a BIRDthay to celebrate!

Made from a hand-carved block, individually hand-pressed and heat embossed, the card will look and feel as personal as the message you choose to write inside. 

Comes with a dark brown envelope and a crystal clear sleeve in a bend-proof mailer for safe shipping. 

Customized and bulk orders are available.
